145
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:52,000
So the goal is to be more contagious.

146
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:59,000
So the bat virus, which was largely a bat virus that sort of first started in China and swept through China, was not the virus that left China.

147
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:03,000
